ak In\n| DirectedBy      = Delyth Thomas\n| WrittenBy       = Victoria Asare-Archer\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|5|22|df=y}}\n| AltDate         = 23 September 2018\n| ShortSummary    = A street girl breaks into the hospital. Not wanting her to get into trouble, Hetty decides to disguise her as a foundling. However the Matron is on the prowl and wants the girl found at all costs.\n\n''' Last Appearance''': Blanche Newbold\n\n| LineColor       = 7A335D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 24\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 4\n| Title           = Land of Opportunity\n| DirectedBy      = Reza Moradi\n| WrittenBy       = Abby Ajayi\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|5|29|df=y}}\n| AltDate         = 23 September 2018\n| ShortSummary    = Many foundlings fall ill. The gang decides to investigate the cause. Meanwhile Hetty decides to find the Matron's secret book and get her terminated.\n| LineColor       = 7A335D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 25\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 5\n| Title           = Dangerous Game\n| DirectedBy      = Reza Moradi\n| WrittenBy       = Gareth Sergeant\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|6|5|df=y}}\n| AltDate         = 30 September 2018\n| ShortSummary    = Vince blackmails Nurse Winterson so he can get special treatment. Meanwhile Hetty learns of a daring visit some of the foundlings are planning.\n\n'''Note''': Ida Battersea returns for this episode\n\n| LineColor       = 7A335D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 26\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 6\n| Title           = Cannon Fodder\n| DirectedBy      = Reza Moradi\n| WrittenBy       = Robin Mukherjee\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|6|12|df=y}}\n| AltDate         = 30 September 2018\n| ShortSummary    = Hetty tries to help Nurse Winterson, but her help ends up landing an innocent man with the label of being a thief.\n\n'''Last Appearance''': Elizabeth Flounder\n\n| LineColor       = 7A335D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 27\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 7\n| Title           = T